				<div class="entry">
	
						<p>Crochet, broderie anglaise, lace and embroidery are big in the summer of 2012, so you might want to try a look that highlights these details. Dresses are the most convenient, but another feminine is piece is of course the skirt, in this case one in a midi-length. Go neon, mix some prints and aim for an expensive Italian look. Don&#8217;t forget your heels and you&#8217;re a masterpiece&#8230;. Ciao bella!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="Midi Skirt - Summer 2012 Outfit Lace skirt, Coral midi skirt Outfit" src="http://i244.photobucket.com/albums/gg11/shiningtrends/crochet-midi-skirt-outfit.jpg" border="0" alt="Midi Skirt - Summer 2012 Outfit Lace skirt, Coral midi skirt Outfit" /></p>
