				<h2><a href="http://www.shiningtrends.com/fashion-chamber/wedding-dresses-with-a-story/" title="Wedding Dresses with a Story">Wedding Dresses with a Story</a></h2>
	
				<div class="postinfo">
	Lizzie - <a href="http://www.shiningtrends.com/category/fashion-chamber/" title="View all posts in Fashion Chamber" rel="category tag">Fashion Chamber</a>  
				</div>
	
				<div class="entry">
	
						<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone" title="Gossip Girl - Vera Wang Wedding Dress - Blair, Gossip Girl - Vera Wang Wedding Dress - Blair" src="http://i244.photobucket.com/albums/gg11/shiningtrends/Gossip-Girl-Blair-Wedding-Dress-vera-wang-1.jpg" border="0" alt="Gossip Girl - Vera Wang Wedding Dress - Blair, Gossip Girl - Vera Wang Wedding Dress - Blair" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">There are some dresses that leave a mark on us and that we remember after time and time. Our wedding dress should make us feel amazing and it&#8217;s so important to get to wear the one that we love. It&#8217;s funny how you can really tell so much about a bride by the dress she chooses. This is why I believe in dresses with a story attached to them.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">This is now so simple and you can have access to amazing dresses easier than even with all the online boutiques out there. I&#8217;ve found an amazing website called <a title="PreOwnedWeddingDresses.com" href="http://www.preownedweddingdresses.com/" target="_blank">PreOwnedWeddingDresses.com</a> that has over 9,000 <a title="used wedding dresses" href="http://www.preownedweddingdresses.com/" target="_blank">used wedding dresses</a> by more than 300 different designers. I&#8217;ve even found Blair&#8217;s Vera Wang wedding dress and lots of great others from Badgley Mischka, Jim Hjerlm, Lazaro or even Oscar de la Renta.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://i244.photobucket.com/albums/gg11/shiningtrends/Badgley-Mischka-worn-wedding-dresses-1.jpg" border="0" alt="Badgley Mischka Wedding Dress, Badgley Mischka Wedding Dress" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">You can filter them properly and make sure you&#8221;ll find the perfect dress for you are you can choose to see dresses by designer, size, price, location or silhouette. There are even some categories that are made available for you to browse for inspiration by checking out the Most Viewed, Best Deals or New Listings of the Week pages. Oh and the website is also a great tool for selling your pretty dress after your wedding so that it can be part of somebody else&#8217;s story.</p>
	
				</div>
	
			</div>
			
